	<h1 class="title">今年流行竞争对手“握手”，美国第二和第三大药店也合并了</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/130051/small/130051.jpg?1435571000" alt="">
